title: DebBrowserVDI
description:
DebBrowser.vdi is a version of Debian Linux 4.0r3 modified for safe web browsing.  Installed applications included Iceweasel (Firefox), MPlayer, MPlayer Mozilla Plugin, MPlayer Codecs, Flash Player, Virtual Machine Additions and the GNU Compliler.  Desktop environments available are Xfce and Flux box.  Runs very well with 384Mb of ram allocated.  256 Mb will do or even less if using Fluxbox.

root user password is debuser.
reg user debuser password is debuser.

You will need Innotek Virtual Box to run this.
